⚙️ Usage in This Project

In this project, the dataset is used for:

Preprocessing MRI images (resizing, normalization)
Feature extraction using deep learning models (CNN / CNN-LSTM / ViT)
Classification of Parkinson’s disease based on brain MRI patterns
